        <section id="return_values" props="electron flutter unity">
            <title>Return Values</title>
            <p props="electron">
                <ul>
                    <li>If the method call succeeds, returns an array of <xref keyref="AudioDeviceInfo"/>, containing the device ID and device name of all audio recording devices.</li>
                    <li>If the method call fails: returns an empty list.</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
            <p props="flutter">
                <ul>
                    <li>If the method call succeeds, returns an array of <xref keyref="AudioDeviceInfo"/> containing the device ID and device name of all audio recording devices.</li>
                    <li>If the method call fails: returns an empty list.</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
            <p props="unity">
                <ul>
                    <li>If the method call succeeds, returns a <xref keyref="VideoDeviceInfo"/> array containing the device ID and device name of all audio recording devices.</li>
                    <li>If the method call fails: <codeph><ph keyref="NULL"/></codeph>.</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
